title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Oct 20 2021

description:
Clay and Buck welcome to the show, former U.S. Deputy Assistant Secretary of Defense for Strategy and Force Development, Elbridge Colby to talk about the China threat. What will be the Biden administration's response if China invades Taiwan? Netflix CEO now says he ‘screwed up’ defending Dave Chappelle in the transgender controversy. Budget reconciliation drama: Manchin tells associates he’s considering leaving the Democratic Party and has an exit plan. What Halloween costume is best for your dog or cat?
